Package: rqrgibbs
Type: Package
Title: Generalized Bayes Interval-Root Regression with Gibbs Sampling
Version: 0.1.0.9003
Authors@R: c(
    person("Antonio", "De Leon", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jaguir26@ucsc.edu"),
    person("Raquel", "Prado", role = "aut"),
    person("Bruno", "Sanso", role = "aut")
  )
Description: Research implementation of loss-based interval regression with
    fixed-design, deep echo-state-network readout, and linear dynamic model
    embeddings. The normal-exponential construction augments an exponentiated
    interval loss and is not a response likelihood.
